reviewText: A Man's Gotta Do is a down to earth comedy with charmingly forlorn and witty songs combined with ironic humour about a man's attempts to understand his daughter .

Great funny Australian film, well worth the money, I really enjoyed the scenes around Kiama  especially the wedding at the old church where I have attended 2 Weddings before.  I would recommend to anyone who has a sense of humour.  Plus the making of the film "Extras" was worth watching too.
